<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَنْ قَتَادَةَ، عَنْ عُروَة <span class="c2">(١)</span>، عَنِ النَّبِيِّ -صلى اللَّه عليه وسلم-.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>رَوَى عَنْهُ أَبُو مُعَاوِيةَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مُرْسَلٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[١٠٨٨٢]</span> مُخْتَارُ بْنُ سَعْدٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>رَوَى عَنْهُ مَعْنُ بْنُ عِيسَى.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
